<sentence id="10">Further , the level of nuclear proteins capable of binding to the NF-kappa B sites in activated T cells increased in response to DM .</sentence>
<sentence id="11">In sum , DM regulates T cell membrane expression of IL-2R by more than one molecular mechanism .</sentence>